headline: Maduro overthrow in oil-rich Venezuela unlikely to shake energy markets in the near term
summary: While Venezuela has the world's largest oil reserves, its oil production is relatively small.

headline: Trump says U.S. oil companies will invest billions of dollars in Venezuela after Maduro’s overthrow
summary: U.S. oil companies will invest billions of dollars in Venezuela's energy sector after the overthrow of Nicolas Maduro, President Donald Trump said.
